"  LEMON CURD:","3  large eggs","6 tablespoons sugar","1 teaspoon grated lemon zest","6 tablespoons strained fresh lemon juice (from about 4 small lemons)","4 tablespoons unsalted butter, cut into 4 pieces","  MERINGUES:","4  large egg whites","1 teaspoon vanilla extract","1 cup plus 1 1/2 tsp. sugar","1 teaspoon white vinegar","1 teaspoon cornstarch","1  pint strawberries, stemmed and sliced"